{"tid":333942,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"「求教學」第一次做貓奴 有咩準備？","createTime":"2017-07-24T09:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T11:18:51.000Z","uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13e21186b3ebbecf9f1eeae689584c512c3ebd73","tid":333942,"uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打好，<br />\n小弟將會成為貓奴，第一次養，<br />\n兩位主子3個月大左右，英短品種，<br />\n<br />\n首先要準備咩？買咩糧會健康岩佢食？<br />\n<br />\n以家可唔可以比罐佢食？？<br />\n<br />\n求攻略心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c71fca3f50354c0bcb92f13f3c4c6d0f6f8af4","tid":333942,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"窗網"},{"pid":"b07c4e9fccb5bf45a78ff994840d6c4facfa45ca","tid":333942,"uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窗網</blockquote>做好<br />\n，而且仲有大部份時間都關窗。"},{"pid":"0bc14927524724859e89b6caf16af0e286b448c2","tid":333942,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"收埋細粒嘅嘢，例如釘，藥丸等<br />\n唔好比佢掂到，會誤食，好大濟"},{"pid":"76502affa6060be81727739135bf505bd228393b","tid":333942,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"貓砂<br />\n市面上好多種類 有礦物砂,豆腐砂,木砂等等<br />\n根據個人喜好同價錢啦 我就用開豆腐砂 價錢中等<br />\n木砂同礦物好似係最平  網上好多寵物用品鋪頭 可以睇睇<br />\n<br />\n乾糧<br />\n3個月有牙仔可以食乾糧, 買幼貓專用既<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得去左診所檢查同打針先<br />\n半歲度就好去絕育 唔係如果貓女 遲下晚晚叫到你無得好訓"},{"pid":"f31ebf4d18ed6df46a77cafdbd564b6501623634","tid":333942,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9649e48aeec40e291ea36f670e93cdf60a1a787d","tid":333942,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"貓砂：可以揀豆腐砂，都好cum到味<br />\n貓糧可以揀D無殼物既貓糧<br />\n<br />\n樓主我有經營網店，比市價平d正貨，有興趣可以tg我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79e2b4e8646f088b9fa7380f98ea6fb3587c065","tid":333942,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"貓中意飲流動既水，可以買水機<br />\n貓玩具逗喵棒果d<br />\n<br />\n恭喜你成為貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8820456734f03cd5b4451c9e390d2fcbcbc9b453","tid":333942,"uid":108103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"最好買佢食開嘅牌子先 食定左再慢慢轉 初到步唔習慣無乜食慾可以試下餵罐頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}